+- [ ] [Core feature 1]
+- [ ] [Core feature 2]
+- [ ] [Core feature 3]
+
+### Phase 3: Verification
+- [ ] Manual testing complete
+- [ ] Edge cases handled
+- [ ] Documentation updated
+<!-- /ANCHOR:phases -->
