+<!-- ANCHOR:milestones -->
+## L3: MILESTONES
+
+| Milestone | Description | Success Criteria | Target |
+|-----------|-------------|------------------|--------|
+| M1 | [Setup Complete] | [All dependencies ready] | [Date/Phase] |
+| M2 | [Core Done] | [Main features working] | [Date/Phase] |
+| M3 | [Release Ready] | [All tests pass] | [Date/Phase] |
+<!-- /ANCHOR:milestones -->
